                        <customfieldvalues>
                            <customfieldvalue>SQL Standard authorization will disable the udfs reflect, reflect2 and java_method by automatically setting the udf blacklist config parameter (hive.server2.builtin.udf.blacklist). However, if HiveServer2 admin chooses to set the config param to a specific value, it will not be altered.&lt;br/&gt;
